## Container Bug Fix (2025-10-13)

Fixed critical bug in OuterClickSensitiveContainer component.

**Bug:**
- `OnParametersSet()` method was calling `base.OnInitialized()` instead of `base.OnParametersSet()`
- This could cause lifecycle issues and unexpected behavior

**Fix:**
```csharp
protected override void OnParametersSet()
{
    base.OnParametersSet();  // Changed from base.OnInitialized()
    BindToLifetime(globalClick.SubscribeForGlobalClick(async e =>
    {
        if (!mouseIn)
        {
            await OnOuterClick();
        }
    }));
}
```

**File Modified:**
- `src/Blazor/DestallMaterials.Blazor.Components/Containers/OuterClickSensitiveContainer.razor`

**Impact:**
- Proper component lifecycle behavior
- Correct base method calls following Blazor best practices

